<figureCitation box="[500,565,799,824]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1392,1414]" captionTargetBox="[157,1431,203,1362]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[155,1432,193,1371]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 3. Maximum clade credibility tree from the Bayesian analyses of Burns et al. (2014). Subfamilies Sporophilinae and Poospizinae shown. Labeling and format as in Fig. 1." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/266314/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="340">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
